Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,還真少見  居然連部長都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.65,0:00:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,妳在這幹什麼 可蕾特同學
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.77,0:00:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  是內卷學長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.51,0:02:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,還問我在幹什麼  難道看不出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,就是完全看不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,她是一年級的可蕾特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,人如其名  是位外國人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不過小時候因為父母的工作而來到了日本
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,已經在這裡生活6到7年了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然半年前她父母回國了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不過可蕾特因為已經適應了這邊的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.79,0:02:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就留下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(1173,990)}locket
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此  是要找吊墜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我還真沒看出來妳是在找東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沒那麼厲害啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是誇你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷學長也幫我找找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,裡面有著我非常重要的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.99,0:02:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,很重要的照片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特  爸爸和媽媽要回國了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你自己一個人會不會很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.99,0:03:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心  只要有這張照片的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,就能感到你們一直都在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.67,0:03:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我也來幫忙吧  那吊墜是怎樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs48}註：日語中火箭和吊墜讀音相近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是不會飛的那種吊墜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,首先我們先去失物認領處看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,造個好箱子哇  鎌倉幕府
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs42}註：いい箱（1185）作ろう鎌倉幕府  日語裡面用「好箱子」諧音「1185」用來記憶鎌倉幕府成立時間  早期曾經用\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h「いい国（1192）作ろう鎌倉幕府」（建個好國家吧鎌倉幕府）後來時間統一成西曆1185年  故有此說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道得真多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,人家很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是小山老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  你們關係真好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs52.5\fsp15\bord0\shad0\c&H1D1920&\pos(789,526.5)\frz298.5}您要不要也進入\N這個世界看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs45\fsp4.5\bord0\shad0\c&H1D1920&\pos(898.5,663)\frz30.11}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同學  找吊墜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,差點忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺大家的失物真是五花八門呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.57,0:04:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,學長  這是宇佐美學姐的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.37,0:04:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.93,0:04:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,居然還丟東西  宇佐美學姐還真冒失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正粗圆_GBK\fs82.5\fax0.2\bord4.5\c&H4CD0EF&\3c&H403427&\shad0\frz355.3\pos(1107,786)}失物招領處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正粗圆_GBK\fs34.5\bord1.5\c&H4CD0EF&\3c&H403427&\shad0\b0\pos(886.5,249)}失物招領處
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不過最關鍵的吊墜不在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的話  只好老老實實來找了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同學還記得你今天去過哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…今天上學後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,先上了天台放風箏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,然後被老師發現後狠狠地教育了一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,然後被拉去指導室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你都幹什麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我是昨天就知道吊墜不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎  那你昨天去過哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這個的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你如此深入調查我的行動模式到底有什麼企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我不幫你囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是內卷和可蕾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.21,0:05:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  丟東西了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,學姐這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.69,0:05:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,幫我撿到了嗎  謝謝可蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎  吊墜不見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  雖然我很想幫你  但是值日生的工作還沒做完
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.59,0:05:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這個我剛剛在走廊上撿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這是部長的?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  如果他來活動室了  麻煩你們交給他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,髮夾變成念珠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就像稻草富翁那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,稻草?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,稻草富翁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,用所持的東西與每次遇到的人交換  讓所持的東西越來越好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.07,0:05:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,最後獲得了巨大的財富
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,因為髮夾變成了念珠  或許部長撿到了吊墜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.71,0:06:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真是積極的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.25,0:06:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,機會主義!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪?  什麼時候不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是宇佐美同學撿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎  待會得跟她說聲謝謝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,快給我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,要給什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,吊墜  你撿到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.61,0:06:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,稻…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,稻草市長先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我是稻草市長先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  我沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\bord5.25\shad0\c&HD97C53&\3c&H824A35&\frz273.2\move(1365,240,1365,270)\fade(0,210)}打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,身為部長  卻完全派不上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.21,0:06:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這跟是不是部長沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這下該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.67,0:06:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就算問我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,只好老老實實地找了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此地毯式尋找也找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那一定不是掉了  而是被偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那吊墜是怎樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  我沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那你昨天去過哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:13.83,Comment,,0,0,0,,就算問我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同學?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,現在我對你們倆的信任嚴重受創
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,再裝下去也沒用  還是坦白從寬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,對了  吊墜就不用找了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,突然怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你口袋裡有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼把口袋翻過來  然後再把手攤開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你那不自然的握拳是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,沒…沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.39,0:08:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼也沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.33,0:08:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,魔術表演時間!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.07,0:08:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好  吊墜盒現在瞬間移動到了我的手裡!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你也太煞費苦心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.05,0:08:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,它原本就裝在口袋裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,按照傳統  我會切腹的  為我介錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs42}註：「介錯」是出自日本歷史上為切腹者來擔當補刀行為之人的稱謂  就是斬首  以讓切腹者更快死亡  免除痛苦折磨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,別鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不過找到了就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是你重要的家人照片吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,可別再弄丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.93,0:08:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷學長真是溫柔!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這種自然流露的溫柔攻陷了她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:08:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,家人的照片?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?  裡面裝的難道不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.51,0:09:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,因為你說這很重要  我便滿以為是你遠方父母的照片…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,上週拍的大頭貼!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然是自己?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体 第二版\fs45\bord0\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HF0E5D4&\b0\frz356.6\pos(1412.142,968.572)}失物招領
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs60\bord4.5\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1418.142,566.572)\frz287.6}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs45\bord4.5\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frz12.63\pos(1467.642,616.072)}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒來!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒來還沒來還沒來!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,難得來一次  可大家都還沒來!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,無聊死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,無聊死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,如果撿鞋不用手  就算我贏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.19,0:10:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  可蕾特同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.39,0:10:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美學姐  你來得太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉  和班上的同學聊著聊著就來遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,都已經糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你看那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,部長怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我在這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.01,0:10:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,睡覺的又不一定是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣的話那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是因為作畫不順利  情緒正低落著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,都這樣一整天了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…不會有事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,部長就這麼一直醒著…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,擔心的是這個?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我說啊  我也是有過一整天醒著的日子的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,部長…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你終於成長了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:25.94,Comment,,0,0,0,,你是在看不起我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:28.57,Comment,,0,0,0,,不不  怎麼可能呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了?  瓶頸期了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.41,0:11:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,該說是遇到瓶頸了呢  還是說才思枯竭呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我在構思我的新老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.99,0:11:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可就是想不到一個好髮型
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,髮型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那  比如說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,短髮波波頭…之類的…怎麼樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(667.5,990)}short bob
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.01,0:11:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣的髮型啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我來告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了  別的啊  可蕾!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我不該提這茬的!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這樣的!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這哪位啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,壽和鮑勃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(862.5,990)}Shou
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(1027.5,990)}Bob
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.99,0:12:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷學長  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是壽和鮑勃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是禿著頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.73,0:12:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  反正我也不抱期待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:24.03,Comment,,0,0,0,,我試著迎合了宇佐美學姐的口味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:25.35,Comment,,0,0,0,,就這幅壽和鮑勃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:27.91,Comment,,0,0,0,,挺不錯的  光頭女生有意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.65,0:12:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他還是喜歡這種類型的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.63,0:12:32.89,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\shad0\c&H688D1C&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fade(0,500)}妹妹在看著你哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,昴哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,請收下我的心吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.69,0:12:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我可做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.63,0:12:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那就明天見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,再見!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs30\bord0\shad0\an7\c&H4839BE&\frz358.2\move(559.5,684,559.5,924)}可愛迷人的\N美髮特集!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.33,0:13:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,拿去參考參考
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,太謝謝你了  我會好好參考的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,隨你參考好啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷學長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,也別忘了這個!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.06,0:14:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,壽和鮑勃就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這並不是短髮波波頭!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,所謂短髮波波頭就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs60\bord4.5\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1739.142,304.072)\frz273.8\b0}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs45\bord4.5\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frz357\pos(1770.642,365.572)}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs52.5\fsp7.5\bord4.5\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frz292.4\pos(1079.142,461.572)\b0}這些都是\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h三次元的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs52.5\fsp7.5\bord4.5\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frz17.92\pos(1178.142,670.072)}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs52.5\bord4.5\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b0\frz288\pos(707.142,649.072)}要不然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn@萝莉体 第二版\fs52.5\bord4.5\shad0\c&H090517&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b0\frz198.2\pos(761.142,703.072)}…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.19,0:14:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,今天去哪裡玩玩嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  小薰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天也得去參加社團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,因為想盡早為下次比賽做好準備
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞希正享受著青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.59,0:14:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我也沒有這個意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是喜歡畫畫而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡畫畫勝過內卷?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀  自然是更喜歡內卷了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  沙耶加  看你讓我說了些什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.81,0:15:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞希你正享受著青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.45,0:15:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞瑞…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,以這種淫亂的理由參加社團活動可不太好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,說什麼淫亂呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們今天就去美術社玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?  別來吧別來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.05,0:15:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊  有什麼不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你們還不是來添亂的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.31,0:15:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不會的不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,非部員本來就不被允許來遊玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.77,0:15:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就作為入部體驗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這個主意不錯  就這麼定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,放過我吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.63,0:15:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來  沙耶加  你的報刊社怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,今日任務  找大新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.45,0:15:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我們部並沒有什麼新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,從沒有新聞的地方創造新聞  這才叫做大新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼要這樣偷偷摸摸的啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你好!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  總覺得好像把怪人帶過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂  居然把摯友叫成怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞瑞這個壞心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:19.35,Comment,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這間活動室還挺普通的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,初次見面  內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我家的瑞希承蒙你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞希是一位心地很善良的好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然有些地方挺淫蕩的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣好嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.25,0:16:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,體驗入社?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我們就是掛著這個名號來蹭玩兒的  別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.03,0:16:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,噓!  涼子  噓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來  今天只有內卷一個人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.89,0:16:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  部長他們去了屋頂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞瑞我問你喔  我可以畫點東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,隨便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:17:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,涼子和沙耶加也畫吧  我們來比賽!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.01,0:17:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,畫得最差的要請飲料!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好  我接受挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那要畫什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,主題是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,居然來這招…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,表情有點僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,兩位  笑一個笑一個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續保持這樣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞瑞你再往右邊靠一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,緊緊依偎在內卷的肩上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.49,0:17:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,因為畫不進去了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,動作快點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就對了嘛~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,感謝我吧  瑞瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,總覺得  看得我都害羞起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.39,0:17:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真抱歉  內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,居然要你陪我做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好  那麼接下來就這樣順勢親個嘴兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你先做示範給我看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.09,0:18:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不要  別這樣  人家還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:23.85,Comment,,0,0,0,,多說無益
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,公佈結果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我要蘋果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.31,0:18:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我要奶茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我要茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那我要喝香蕉歐蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.63,0:18:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的畫得那麼差嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我買回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,危險  危險
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.95,0:19:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,香蕉歐蕾賣完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,可樂  給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.43,0:19:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  內卷不能喝碳酸飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺有點可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.91,0:19:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.53,0:19:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.49,0:19:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然這罐我嘴巴碰過了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不介意的話要和我的交換嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.81,0:19:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不不  說實在那有點太…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  內卷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯你個頭  那罐是人家喝過的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.69,0:19:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,換句話說  就是間…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,間?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,間接接吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,太遲鈍了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,薰你也說點什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我本來是開開玩笑而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那罐明明是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.11,0:20:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉  我全都喝光了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.17,0:20:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,內卷  那罐是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:20:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一來我們就扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?  你看起來好像也不怎麼不甘心耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?  沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.47,0:21:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好受打擊哇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.05,0:21:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.11,0:21:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,當然是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  秀恩愛的你們快給我爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然是間接的  但是也是接過吻了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,薰她們今天過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,說不定挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.85,0:22:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.13,0:22:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.97,0:22:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,沙耶加!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.17,0:23:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真不好意思  我居然在發呆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.19,0:23:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,作為處罰我到走廊上罰站
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.45,0:23:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.43,0:23:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我才想問好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.73,0:23:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我不是什麼可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.95,0:23:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我是美術社的顧問  立花夢子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.23,0:23:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,意思是說不把我當作顧問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.87,0:23:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛似乎有點像老師了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.39,0:23:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是不良少年嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.43,0:23:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好  好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.03,0:24:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我去外面吸一下新鮮空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.51,0:24:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.71,0:24:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有變態!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.63,0:24:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,下集  這個美術社大有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.37,0:24:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微去散步  敬請期待
